
<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>Some time in the middle of 2017, Ruby (my girlfriend) and I decided it was time to take a trip to explore the southern part of Mexico, our North American neighbor. The trip too place in between February 21 and March 4, 2018 and spanned multiple cities in the Mexican states of Chiapas and Quintana Roo. Our three main stops were San Christobal de las Casas (Chiapas), Palenque (Chiapas), and the coastal city of Tulum (Quintana Roo).</p>

